  : 2. Lifetime '*arena<ctx>' must outlive '*arena'
  .
 ... caused by 1.
  -> 'int*arena' assigned to pointer with lifetime '*arena<ctx>'
  :
 == note: pointee 'int' is lifetime-permissive, its lifetime may be shortened.
  .
 ... caused by 2.
  -> '*arena<outer>' lifetime is greater than '*arena<inner>'
  :
 == note: '*arena<inner>' defined here
  :     arena {
  :     ^^^^^^^  --- nested_arenas.rna:4:5
